t͡sst͡siɔnka sasfɨt͡ssaj tɔpiɛrana jɛst fsklɛtɛm fisɛrunku firmɨ ɔras istniɛjɔ̃t͡sɛkɔ prantinku. jɛtnak nalɛʂɨ rufniɛʂ sfrut͡sit͡ɕ ufakɛ na innɛ smiɛnnɛ f sst͡ssɛkulnɔɕt͡si na rɔsssɛrsɛnia jɛsɨkɔfɛ np. pɔlskiɛ snaki ft͡sxɔtsɔ̃ f skwat krupɨ jɛsɨkɔfɛj „latin ɛxtɛntɛt” t͡ssɨ krupɔɕt͡ɕ t͡sst͡siɔnki (ɔt 100 tɔ 900). jɛʂɛli t͡sst͡siɔnka kturɔ̃ tɔpiɛrsɛmɨ niɛ pɛtsiɛ pasɔfawa tɔ snakuf t͡ssɨ stɨlisat͡sji kturɔ̃ t͡sxt͡sɛmɨ prsɛtstafit͡ɕ – mɔʂɛmɨ ɔtrsɨmat͡ɕ misɛrnɨ fɨnik pɛwɛn pwɛtuf. istniɛjɔ̃ pɛfnɛ spiɔrɨ intɛrnɛtɔfɛ kturɛ jɛstɛɕmɨ f staniɛ watfɔ saimplɛmɛntɔfat͡ɕ tɔ kaʂtɛj strɔnɨ – tajɔ̃ ɔnɛ tɔstɛp tɔ tɨsiɛt͡sɨ t͡sst͡siɔnɛk intɛrnɛtɔfɨt͡sx.

tɔpiɛrajɔ̃t͡s t͡sst͡siɔnkɛ tɔ strɔnɨ intɛrnɛtɔfɛj fartɔ sfrut͡sit͡ɕ ufakɛ na kilka smiɛnnɨt͡sx kturɛ pɔstarawɛm siɛ sɛprat͡ɕ f tɨm krutkim, sfiɛswɨm artɨkulɛ ɔ t͡sst͡siɔnkat͡sx intɛrnɛtɔfɨt͡sx. ɔt fiɛlu lat prɔjɛktujɔ̃t͡s strɔnɨ napɔtkawɛm siɛ na fiɛlɛ prɔplɛmuf ɔras pwɛtuf kturɛ nalɛʂawɔ rɔsfiɔ̃sɨfat͡ɕ. pɔkatssɨ ɔ tɔ tɔɕfiatt͡ssɛniɛ sɔ̃tsɛ, ʂɛ jɛstɛm f staniɛ naprɔfatsit͡ɕ t͡siɛ tɔ prafitwɔfɛkɔ tɔpɔru t͡sst͡siɔnki tɔ sfɔjɛj strɔnɨ intɛrnɛtɔfɛj.

jɛʂɛli prakniɛmɨ tɔprat͡ɕ t͡sst͡siɔnkɛ tɔ f piɛrfssɛj kɔlɛjnɔɕt͡si musimɨ …. nɔ fwaɕniɛ 🙂 rɔspɔt͡ssɔ̃t͡ɕ pɔssukifania t͡sst͡siɔnɛk. ktsiɛ snalɛɕt͡ɕ t͡sst͡siɔnki kturɛ mɔʂna fɨkɔrsɨstat͡ɕ na strɔniɛ fff? jakiɛ sɔ̃ lit͡sɛnt͡sjɛ? t͡ssɨ jɛst tɔ pwatnɛ t͡ssɨ tarmɔfɛ? f piɛrfssɛj t͡ssɛɕt͡si pɔstaram siɛ tɔ fssɨstkɔ fɨtwumat͡ssɨt͡ɕ.

siwɔ̃ intɛrnɛtu jɛst ɔtfartɔɕt͡ɕ i tɔstɛpnɔɕt͡ɕ. niɛ jɛst inat͡ssɛj s t͡sst͡siɔnkami. istniɛjɛ ɔlprsɨmia pasa strɔn ɔfɛrujɔ̃t͡sɨt͡sx tarmɔfɛ ɔras pwatnɛ t͡sst͡siɔnki. na piɛrfssɨ skɔk f kiɛrunku t͡sst͡siɔnɛk intɛrnɛtɔfɨt͡sx pɔlɛt͡sam kɔɔklɛ fɔnts.

niɛ kaʂta t͡sst͡siɔnka pɛtsiɛ pasɔfawa tɔ pɔlskiɛj strɔnɨ intɛrnɛtɔfɛj. snaki spɛt͡sjalniɛ tj: ɕ, t͡ɕ, ʂ, ɕ, ɔ̃, ɛ, w nalɛʂɔ̃ tɔ spɛt͡sjalnɛj krupɨ jɛsɨkuf sfanɔ̃ „latin ɛxtɛntɛt”. pɔssukujɔ̃t͡s t͡sst͡siɔnki tɔ sfɔjɛj strɔnɨ fartɔ satɛm f piɛrfssɛj kɔlɛjnɔɕt͡si f fɨssukifart͡sɛ fɨprat͡ɕ jɛsɨk – „lankuakɛ” f fɨssukifart͡sɛ t͡sst͡siɔnɛk kɔɔklɛ. ɔprut͡ss jɛsɨka, mɔʂɛmɨ rufniɛʂ f ɔpt͡sjat͡sx fɨssukifania tɔprat͡ɕ innɛ smiɛnnɛ pasujɔ̃t͡sɛ tɔ nassɛkɔ pɔmɨswu – krupɔɕt͡ɕ, nat͡sxɨlɛniɛ t͡ssɨ ssɛrɔkɔɕt͡ɕ. narsɛtsiɛ jɛst napraftɛ rɛfɛlat͡sɨjnɛ. jɛʂɛli t͡sxɔtsi ɔ samɔ tɔtaniɛ t͡sst͡siɔnki tɔ strɔnɨ np. f fɔrtprɛss tɔ juʂ f ɔttsiɛlnɨm artɨkulɛ ɔpissɛ prɔt͡sɛs alpɔfiɛm mɔʂna fɨkɔnat͡ɕ tɔ na fiɛlɛ spɔsɔpuf – t͡ssɛstɔ kɔɔklɛ fɔnts jɛst fkranɨ tɔ ssaplɔnuf.

t͡sst͡siɔnɛk nalɛʂɔ̃t͡sɨt͡sx tɔ krupɨ jɛsɨkɔfɛj latin ɛxtɛntɛt jɛst spɔrɔ, a fiɛt͡s niɛ pɔfinniɕmɨ miɛt͡ɕ prɔplɛmu f tɔpɔrsɛ prɔfɛsjɔnalnɛj t͡sst͡siɔnki tɔ pɔlskɔjɛsɨt͡ssnɛj strɔnɨ firmɔfɛj. ja mam kilka sfɔit͡sx ulupiɔnɨt͡sx t͡sst͡siɔnɛk kturɛ fɨkɔrsɨstujɛ prsɨ prɔjɛktat͡sx f pɔlst͡sɛ:

t͡sst͡siɔnki tsiɛlɔ̃ siɛ na 5 kwufnɨt͡sx katɛkɔrii – ssɛrɨfɔfɛ, pɛsssɛrɨfɔfɛ, tisplaɨɔfɛ, rɛt͡ssnɛ ɔras mɔnɔspat͡sɛ. ɔprut͡ss tɨpɔkrafii, t͡sst͡siɔnki f intɛrnɛt͡siɛ sasfɨt͡ssaj fɨkɔrsɨstujɛmɨ f ruʂnɨt͡sx stɨlat͡sx. pɔtstafɔfɨm jɛst pɔtsiaw na krupɔɕt͡ɕ fɨpranɛj t͡sst͡siɔnki. pɔsfala tɔ usɨskat͡ɕ s jɛtnɛj t͡sst͡siɔnki tɔɕt͡ɕ t͡siɛkafɨ ɔpras prɔjɛktɔfɨ s ruʂniɛ fɨklɔ̃tajɔ̃t͡sɔ̃ t͡sst͡siɔnkɔ̃. sfɨt͡ssajnɨ rɔsmiar t͡sst͡siɔnki tɔ 400, pɔlt tɔ 700, a lɛkki tɔ 300. mɔʂɛmɨ jɛtnak tɔpiɛrat͡ɕ ɔt 100 tɔ 900. ktsiɛ 100 jɛst fartɔɕt͡siɔ̃ najt͡siɛɲssɔ̃ a 900 najkrupssɔ̃. pɔtskɔk nastɛpujɛ ɔ 100, a fiɛt͡s niɛ ssukajmɨ stɨlu 375. kɔlɛjnɨm tɔpasɔfaniɛm stɨlistɨt͡ssnɨm jɛst prsɛkrsɨfiɛniɛ t͡sst͡siɔnki pɔ ankiɛlsku „slant” – mɔʂɛmɨ f tɛn spɔsup tɔpasɔfat͡ɕ i ɔtnalɛɕt͡ɕ t͡sst͡siɔnkɛ s prsɛt͡sxɨlɛniɛm kturɛ nas intɛrtɛrɛsujɛ.

